&reftitle.description;
arrayarray_uintersect arrayarray arrayarrays callablevalue_compare_func
Calcula la intersección de dos arrays, compara los datos utilizando una función de retrollamada.

&reftitle.parameters;




   array



     El primer array.





   arrays



     Arrays a comparar contra





   value_compare_func

    &sort.callback.description;
    &sort.callback.description.presort;

  &reftitle.examples;



    Ejemplo con array_uintersect


<?php
$array1 = array("a" => "green", "b" => "brown", "c" => "blue", "red");
$array2 = array("a" => "GREEN", "B" => "brown", "yellow", "red");

print_r(array_uintersect($array1, $array2, "strcasecmp"));
?>


    &example.outputs;


Array
(
    [a] => green
    [b] => brown
    [0] => red
)
